SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (EI) REGULATIONS, to amend the eligibility criteria so that claimants who have current return to work action plans that call for training to which they have not yet been referred by the prescribed deadlines will be able to participate in Pilot Porject No. 14.
